  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "I promised myself last week that I would finally write down my full class schedule, so here it is, hour by hour.",
      "zh": "我上星期跟自己保證要把完整的課表寫下來，所以就是這篇，一節一節寫。"
    },
    {
      "en": "School starts at eight o'clock sharp, and the clock in our classroom is somehow always five minutes slow.",
      "zh": "學校八點整開始上課，而我們教室的時鐘不知為何永遠慢五分鐘。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The first class of the morning is science, which lasts a full hour and usually includes at least one small experiment.",
      "zh": "早上第一堂課是自然課，整整一小時，通常至少會有一個小實驗。"
    },
    {
      "en": "After science comes history, where we are currently learning about events from a few hundred years ago.",
      "zh": "自然課之後是歷史課，我們現在正在學幾百年前發生的事件。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Our history teacher once said that a thousand small choices add up to change a whole country, which I still think about sometimes.",
      "zh": "我們歷史老師曾經說，一千個小小的選擇加起來就能改變整個國家，我到現在有時候還會想起這句話。"
    },
    {
      "en": "At exactly ten thirty, we get a short break, and half the class runs straight to the vending machine before it eats their coins.",
      "zh": "十點半整，我們有一段短暫的下課時間，班上一半的人會直接衝去自動販賣機，趁它還沒把硬幣吃掉之前。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The third class before noon is art, my personal favorite, where the teacher lets us choose any color we want.",
      "zh": "中午前的第三堂課是美術，我最喜歡的一堂課，老師讓我們自己選喜歡的顏色。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Lunch happens right at noon, and by that point, I am always extremely hungry, no matter how big my breakfast was.",
      "zh": "午餐正好在中午，到那個時候我總是餓得要命，不管早餐吃了多少都一樣。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The first afternoon class is music, where we are learning to sing a simple song as a whole class.",
      "zh": "下午第一堂課是音樂課，我們正在學一首簡單的歌，全班一起唱。"
    },
    {
      "en": "At one thirty, we have computer class, and last week the whole computer lab lost power for about a quarter of an hour.",
      "zh": "下午一點半是電腦課，上星期整間電腦教室停電了大概一刻鐘。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The final class of the day usually ends around three o'clock, though on Wednesdays it ends an hour earlier.",
      "zh": "一天最後一堂課通常是三點結束，不過星期三會提早一小時結束。"
    },
    {
      "en": "After school, I have about a half hour before I need to walk home, so I usually spend it talking with Bernice.",
      "zh": "放學後，我大概有半小時可以走回家，我通常會拿這段時間跟 Bernice 聊天。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice's own schedule is almost exactly the same as mine, except her school gives an extra music class on Fridays.",
      "zh": "Bernice 自己的課表跟我幾乎一模一樣，只是她們學校星期五多一堂音樂課。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the time I get home, it is usually a little past four in the afternoon, and William is already home from his own school.",
      "zh": "我到家的時候通常已經下午四點多了，William 早就從他自己的學校放學回家了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Homework time officially starts at five o'clock, though it always seems to actually start closer to five thirty.",
      "zh": "功課時間正式從五點開始，不過實際上總是要拖到五點半左右才真的開始。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Dinner is at exactly seven, and by nine o'clock, Sophia is already telling everyone it is time to think about bed.",
      "zh": "晚餐是準時七點，到了九點，Sophia 就已經開始跟大家說該想想要準備睡覺了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Looking at my whole schedule written out like this, my day feels a lot longer than I usually think it is.",
      "zh": "把整個課表這樣寫出來看，我的一天感覺比我平常想的還要長很多。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William asked to see my schedule and said his own day is much simpler: school, snacks, and robots, in that exact order.",
      "zh": "William 要求看我的課表，說他自己的一天簡單多了：上學、吃點心，然後機器人，順序就是這樣。"
    }
  ],
